========================================================
 Basque Named Entities Corpus for in domain Basque NERC
========================================================

This dataset contains sentences from the news domain with manually annotated 
named entities. The data is the merge of EIEC (a dataset of a collection of 
news wire articles from Euskaldunon Egunkaria newspaper, (Alegria et al. 2004)), 
and newly annotated data from naiz.eus.

# Dataset format and distribution
# ----------------

# The dataset is divided into three files: train / test and validation splits. 

51,539 train.jsonl (News)
12,936 val.jsonl (News)
35,855 test.jsonl (News)

Tagged named entities are classified into 4 categories: person (PER),
location (LOC), organization (ORG) and other (MISC) named entities that
do not belong to the previous 3 groups.


